00:53:31,960 --> 00:53:33,109
Have a nice time.

844
00:53:33,200 --> 00:53:35,509
Actually, Nicholas,
you might as well take a break.

845
00:53:35,600 --> 00:53:38,273
Hey, great. I've got something to show you.

