857
00:54:40,760 --> 00:54:42,876
Danny, believe me,
it's not something you ever get used to.

858
00:54:42,960 --> 00:54:45,110
Yeah. Maybe we should
go on the bouncy castle.

859
00:54:45,200 --> 00:54:46,235
