888
00:57:28,520 --> 00:57:32,354
- Are you saying that this is a crime scene?
- Yes, sir, I am.

889
00:57:32,440 --> 00:57:33,759
Very well.

890
00:57:34,280 --> 00:57:35,315
- Detectives.
- Sir.

891
00:57:35,400 --> 00:57:36,913
